{"type":"message","id":"f2f573c1","parentId":"ddf3da07","timestamp":"2026-04-18T09:52:04.281Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Lead is getting ERR_CONNECTION_REFUSED on port 5002. They're running on local machine while I started the services on the VPS. The Lead needs to run the projects on their local machine, not on the VPS.\n\nLet me check what port the FE is trying to connect to and explain the situation.","thinkingSignature":"caed050f4159308763b53e2be0b7f3bbf47eaacf2521ad1f049ea2263e35d754"},{"type":"text","text":"Hiểu rồi! Mình chạy trên VPS còn Lead chạy trên local. Trên local Lead cần:\n\n**1. Pull code mới nhất về local:**\n```bash\n# QLHV BE\ncd ~/ahv-qlhv-be\ngit fetch origin\ngit checkout feat/exam-results-enhancement\nyarn build\nyarn start\n\n# QLHV FE  \ncd ~/ahv-qlhv-fe\ngit fetch origin\ngit checkout feat/exam-results-enhancement\nyarn build\nyarn start\n```\n\n**2. Đảm bảo MongoDB local đang chạy** (port 27017)\n\n**3. Tạo file `.env` ở BE local** với:\n```\nMONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/qlhv\nPORT=5555\nJWT_SECRET=...\nFRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000\n```\n\nHoặc nếu Lead muốn mình start trên VPS để Lead truy cập từ xa, mình cần biết **IP/domain VPS** của Lead để config CORS + URL đúng.\n\nLead đang chạy local hay muốn mình host trên VPS?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":56,"output":335,"cacheRead":61520,"cacheWrite":1158,"totalTokens":63069,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776505909830,"responseId":"063287384f6980cfbcd3c3aef00135bb"}}
