{"type":"message","id":"fc317799","parentId":"7861c5f9","timestamp":"2026-04-18T10:18:31.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The build clearly contains all the new features:\n1. `ImportResultsModal` - confirmed (shows the full modal UI)\n2. `absentCount` (Vắng) - confirmed (`a.studentResults?.filter(a=>\"absent\"===a.result).length||0` and `children:o` for Vắng)\n3. Import button - confirmed (`\" Import\"` button)\n4. theoryResult, simulationResult, parkingResult, roadResult - confirmed in `openResultModal`\n\nThe build is definitely correct. The issue must be that the user is seeing a cached version. Maybe Next.js is serving a cached static page.\n\n\nI should verify the server is actually running on port 3000 and serving the updated code, since Next.js caches pages aggressively. The `yarn start` command should be running the production build, which is what I need to check.","thinkingSignature":"53926c76d1de69b760ef37f46152bc242ef5b3d571ce65c6858c59f28b1ed3ee"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wor4afib2xkk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ss -tlnp | grep \":3000\" && echo \"---\" && curl -s http://localhost:3000/api/v1/roles 2>&1 | head -3","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":7954,"output":253,"cacheRead":84523,"cacheWrite":714,"totalTokens":93444,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776507502425,"responseId":"06328d6f812e15344bb08127e818d749"}}
