{"type":"message","id":"35fd8aba","parentId":"7a9b79e3","timestamp":"2026-04-18T10:20:49.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see requests to the BE from the user's IP, but no `/api/v1/exam-batches` requests. The FE isn't making the exam-batches API call. Let me check if the sat-hach page is making the right API calls. Let me check if the user is even hitting the exam-batches endpoint.\n\nActually wait - the user's IP is 116.98.243.87, and I can see requests. But I don't see `/api/v1/exam-batches` calls. The sat-hach page calls `getExamBatches(1, 50)` which should hit `/api/v1/exam-batches`. \n\nThe FE might not be loading the sat-hach page properly, or the exam-batches route isn't being registered correctly. Let me verify the endpoint exists and check what routes are actually available in the BE.","thinkingSignature":"6c24514cd8f437125047d4b2c530308e75a84f338bb5c8ddfef14f821b4e6040"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wifoqdozldvb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -H \"Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZTM1NzBiNDI4MzU4MmMzNjliZDMxNCIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50Iiwicm9sZXMiOlsic3R1ZGVudCJdLCJhZ2VudF9pZCI6bnVsbCwiaWF0IjoxNzc2NTA3MDc1LCJleHAiOjE3NzY1OTM0NzV9.lNnXeg3P0wnyFCN-3jb-pL1uGXCQzaZwW_ehnR-KF4o\" \"http://localhost:5555/api/v1/exam-batches?page=1&limit=50\" 2>&1 | head -200","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1278,"output":412,"cacheRead":99390,"cacheWrite":217,"totalTokens":101297,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776507638930,"responseId":"06328df8e28cc570899c50170d16e6d3"}}
