{"type":"message","id":"d1eec28a","parentId":"a4d75881","timestamp":"2026-04-18T10:28:18.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that `res.sendFile` uses `process.cwd()` but that might not resolve the path correctly with `dist/`. Let me just use an absolute path or use `path.resolve`.Actually, looking at the error, it seems like `res.sendFile` can't find the file even though the path exists. This is likely a permission issue or the path resolution is wrong. Let me try using `path.resolve` instead.Let me just use a simpler approach - send the file manually using `res.download`.","thinkingSignature":"b8226faa72a3613169912df795510ae1bbced0aa1234173840e6aea45c1585ce"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_klys2q9o7l69_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/exam_import.controller.ts","edits":[{"oldText":"export const downloadSampleTemplate = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const path = require('path');\n  const fs = require('fs');\n\n  const samplePath = path.join(process.cwd(), 'dist/src/interface/docs/mau_import_ket_qua_thi.xlsx');\n  \n  if (!fs.existsSync(samplePath)) {\n    return res.statusError('Sample file not found', 404);\n  }\n\n  res.setHeader('Content-Disposition', 'attachment; filename=\"mau_import_ket_qua_thi.xlsx\"');\n  res.setHeader('Content-Type', 'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet');\n  res.sendFile(samplePath);\n});","newText":"export const downloadSampleTemplate = catchAsync(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {\n  const path = require('path');\n  const fs = require('fs');\n\n  const samplePath = path.resolve(process.cwd(), 'src/interface/docs/mau_import_ket_qua_thi.xlsx');\n  \n  if (!fs.existsSync(samplePath)) {\n    return res.statusError('Sample file not found', 404);\n  }\n\n  res.download(samplePath, 'mau_import_ket_qua_thi.xlsx');\n});"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1144,"output":470,"cacheRead":115663,"cacheWrite":253,"totalTokens":117530,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776508085933,"responseId":"06328fb79182dc5afb1a86f86699d230"}}
