{"type":"message","id":"53d8ea10","parentId":"aab4a41b","timestamp":"2026-04-18T10:32:17.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants a chart/visualization for exam results on the sat-hach page. Let me implement this - a bar/pie chart showing pass/fail/absent breakdown by section (theory, simulation, parking, road).\n\nI'll add a chart component using recharts (which is likely already installed in the project) or chart.js.","thinkingSignature":"a3e84659970d2e61cddd63750eb96a74cb953a0572cd4e603dc647167ae32f8b"},{"type":"text","text":"Đang thêm biểu đồ thống kê. Check thư viện chart có sẵn không:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e3tyitbizl3g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -E \"recharts|chart\\.js|chartjs|apexcharts\" /root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/package.json","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":174,"cacheRead":121752,"cacheWrite":412,"totalTokens":122338,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776508328527,"responseId":"063290aa00f7d9eea9e2a7864ae9c5f8"}}
