{"type":"message","id":"1dce08df","parentId":"60f33a77","timestamp":"2026-04-18T10:49:16.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The new code IS in the SSR bundle. So the chart code is there. The issue might be browser cache. Let me tell Lead to do a hard refresh. But also, the exam batch in the database might not have the new schema fields (failedBySection, etc.) because it was created before the new schema.\n\nActually, the chart calculates failedBySection from the existing `studentResults` data, so it should work. The issue might be that Lead hasn't opened the exam batch panel yet.\n\nLet me also verify the BE is running correctly and the data has the right format.","thinkingSignature":"599484017c5441468d28f005ac0a1529fcc2f389bc5a48dc93250b03cbf340ba"},{"type":"text","text":"Code mới đã có trong server. Kiểm tra dữ liệu:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_17b5aiosx28p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"RESP=$(curl -s -X POST \"http://localhost:5555/api/v1/auth/login\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"username\":\"admin@qlhv.vn\",\"password\":\"Admin@123456\"}') && TOKEN=$(echo \"$RESP\" | grep -o '\"token\":\"[^\"]*\"' | cut -d'\"' -f4) && curl -s -H \"Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN\" \"http://localhost:5555/api/v1/exam-batches/69e35b0a555e3a1476a6f1e1\" | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -30","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":97,"output":314,"cacheRead":133465,"cacheWrite":641,"totalTokens":134517,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776509347667,"responseId":"063294a573191349d0cfcc7fbe118a17"}}
